<h3 id="file-steganography">File Steganography</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Can you open it?</li>
  <li><code>file filename</code> can usually identify the type</li>
  <li>Try checking the magic bytes</li>
  <li>check file type</li>
  <li>If it is an image:
    <ul>
      <li>binwalk</li>
      <li>check</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

